---
title: Pea and Pesto Orzo with cheese and chilli garnish
description: This cheesy pesto orzo tastes deliciously rich but not overly so. The addition of chilli cuts through with perfectly-proportioned spice. This is a hearty and comforting dish that's perfect for any occasion.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R10_W45_IE_IEXCVCLV0085-20_Main_high-80c96ea5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/spicy-courgette-risotto-62f4d73b1947871a9ae41690-74a2a1a7.pdf
author: HelloFresh
